para_trans: Hon'ble Minister of State for Government
Government Decision No. -Shaniva-1525 / Q. No.27 / Niwas-2
Reference - General Administration Department, Government Decision No. -Shaniva-1524 / Q. No. 312 / Niwas-2 dated - 23rd December 2024
Smt.Meghna Deepak Sakore-Bordikar, Hon'ble Minister of State to Ms.Suniti-06, Churchgate, Mumbai
The decision to allot this government accommodation, which was taken under the relevant government decision, has now been cancelled.
Smt. Meghna Deepak Sakore-Bordikar, Hon'ble Minister of State has been allotted Government Residence Avanti-05 at Malabar Hill instead of Government Residence Suniti-06 at Churchgate.
The government has taken a decision.
The residence allotted to the Hon'ble Minister of State shall be compulsorily vacated within a period of fifteen days from the date of her discharge from office.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
